# ============================================
# API CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# Backend API base URL
# IMPORTANT:
#   - Do NOT include trailing slashes
#   - Do NOT include /api in the URL (it's added automatically)
#   - Must match the backend server PORT and host
#
# Format: http://host:port or https://host:port
#
# Examples:
#   Local development: http://localhost:3000
#   Production: https://api.yourdomain.com
#   Custom port: http://localhost:5000
#
# Note: The axios instance automatically appends /api to this URL
#       So http://localhost:3000 becomes http://localhost:3000/api
# ============================================
VITE_API_URL=